You are implementing a Blazor Web App for a logistics company that tracks shipments. The project has already been scaffolded at `/tmp/sv-3e9b4d4244e141b28701a08787d0aae4/ShipmentTracker/` using `dotnet new blazor -int Auto -ai -au Individual`.

